  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Cheerful Afghan Winter &amp; Summer</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">After a successful winter program we have now expanded our activities and campaign to the summer. Everyday 1500 children in Kabul, Herat, Mazaresharif, Bamyan, Khost and Nanagarhar are enjoying many different social, fun, healing and educative activities. It is difficult to be a child in Afghanistan especially for the underprivileged ones such as children of refugee camps, orphanages and street-working children.  We provide them different classes, arts, social skills and first of all hope.</narrative>
  </description>
